---
// Contacto.astro
---

<section id="contacto" class="py-24 px-6 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-['Cinzel_Decorative'] text-4xl md:text-5xl text-emerald-950 mb-4">
        Contacta con Nosotros
      </h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-[#D4A259] mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Estamos aquí para ayudarte a encontrar la pieza perfecta. Escríbenos o síguenos en nuestras redes sociales.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      
      <a 
        href="https://www.instagram.com/ambar.bisuteriaycomplementos/" 
        target="_blank" 
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group border border-slate-100"
      >
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-900 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#D4A259] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect>
            <path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path>
            <line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-2">Instagram</h3>
        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm text-center group-hover:text-[#D4A259] transition-colors">@ambar.bisuteriaycomplementos</span>
      </a>

      <a 
        href="https://www.facebook.com/people/Ambar-Bisuteria-y-Complementos/61585072056170/?fb_profile_edit_entry_point=%7B%22click_point%22%3A%22edit_profile_button%22%2C%22feature%22%3A%22profile_header%22%7D&sk=about&locale=es_ES" 
        target="_blank" 
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group border border-slate-100"
      >
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-900 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#D4A259] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-2">Facebook</h3>
        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm text-center group-hover:text-[#D4A259] transition-colors">Ámbar Bisutería</span>
      </a>

      <a 
        href="tel:+34642147088" 
        class="flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group border border-slate-100"
      >
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-900 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#D4A259] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-2">Teléfono</h3>
        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm text-center group-hover:text-[#D4A259] transition-colors">+34 642 14 70 88</span>
      </a>

      <a 
        href="mailto:ambar.bisuteriacomplementos@gmail.com" 
        class="flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group border border-slate-100"
      >
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-900 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#D4A259] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-2">Email</h3>
        <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm text-center break-all px-2 group-hover:text-[#D4A259] transition-colors">ambar.bisuteriacomplementos<br/>@gmail.com</span>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>